{"tid":1913364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實依家重有冇人諗移民？","createTime":"2020-03-06T17:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T17:19:56.000Z","uid":229185,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9eaa914fe10c4fe1f64df3cb660316d57cff696d","tid":1913364,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:09:06.000Z","msg":"諗住去美國，原來睇個醫生都萬幾蚊，我估都會爆到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 侵侵： 唔洗戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n諗住去加拿大， 咁近美國， 都唔知會唔會仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗住去英國， 歐洲又爆到7彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗住去日本南韓， 日本南韓都係仆哂街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗住去台灣， 台灣人工計係港紙都係5000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （除左新北市好似幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n諗住去澳洲， 紫外光射到你生癌症<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上排華排亞洲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗嚟諗去， 我諗到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xnW2BRy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxnW2BRy.jpg&h=358cbacd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c6b9b8551630bcf7976ae2429a6b6935ec856fe","tid":1913364,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:14:02.000Z","msg":"<